<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>outcomestar — Every outcome. One star.</title>
<meta name="description" content="OutcomeStar is a lifelong record of your child's academic, athletic, and personal achievements — one place to capture everything, so college applications, resumes, and recruiting profiles fill themselves later. For parents of kids ages 0–18.">
